#. Tag: title
#: mainworkspace.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Main Work Space is normally organized with the View Selector to the left "
"and the data view to the right."
msgstr ""
"Glavni delovni prostor je običajno organiziran z izbirnikom pogleda na levi "
"in pogledom podatkov na desni."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As usual, you will also find the Menu bar and Toolbar at the top, and the "
"Status bar at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Kot običajno boste na vrhu našli tudi menijsko vrstico in orodno vrstico, na "
"dnu pa vrstico stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since both the View selector and the Scripts docker are dockers they can be "
"moved to the different border, floated or hidden. To show a hidden docker, "
"use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dockers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Ker sta izbirnik pogleda in okence za skripte okna, ju je mogoče premakniti "
"na drugo obrobo, lebdeti ali skriti. Če želite prikazati skrito sidrišče za "
"okna, uporabite menijski vnos <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Sidrišča</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: mainworkspace.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Selector"
msgstr "Izbirnik pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"the-view-selector\">View Selector</link> enables you to "
"select the data view you want to display from the currently listed views."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"the-view-selector\">Izbirnik pogleda</link> vam omogoča, da "
"med trenutno navedenimi pogledi izberete pogled podatkov, ki ga želite "
"prikazati."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Views are grouped into categories for easier retrieval: Editors, Views, "
"Execution and Reports by default:"
msgstr ""
"Pogledi so razvrščeni v kategorije za lažje iskanje: privzeto urejevalniki, "
"pogledi, izvajanje in poročila:"

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Editors holds the editors that you need to define and schedule your project."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalniki vsebuje urejevalnike, ki jih potrebujete za definiranje in "
"načrtovanje vašega projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Views holds views that are used for inspecting your project."
msgstr ""
"Pogledi vsebujejo poglede, ki se uporabljajo za pregled vašega projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Execution holds views that are especially useful during the execution of "
"your project."
msgstr ""
"Izvedba vsebuje poglede, ki so še posebej uporabni med izvajanjem vašega "
"projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reports holds views for report generation."
msgstr "Poročila vsebujejo poglede za ustvarjanje poročil."

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Views can also be moved within or across categories, or added to or removed "
"from the <link linkend=\"the-view-selector\">View Selector</link>."
msgstr ""
"Poglede je mogoče tudi premikati znotraj kategorij ali med njimi ali jih "
"dodati ali odstraniti iz <link linkend=\"the-view-selector\">izbirnika "
"pogledov</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: mainworkspace.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedule Selector"
msgstr "Izbirnik časovnega plana"

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Schedule Selector enables you to select the schedule all the views (&eg; "
"<link linkend=\"task-gantt-view\">Gantt View</link>) shall display values "
"from. Tasks which has not been scheduled in the selected schedule are not "
"normally shown in any of the views. (They are shown in editors, of course.)"
msgstr ""
"Izbirnik časovnega plana vam omogoča, da izberete plan, iz katerega bodo "
"prikazane vrednosti vseh pogledov (&eg; <link linkend=\"task-gantt-view"
"\">Ganttov pogled</link>). Naloge, ki niso bile načrtovane v izbranem "
"urniku, običajno niso prikazane v nobenem pogledu. (Seveda so prikazane v "
"urejevalnikih.)"

#. Tag: title
#: mainworkspace.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status Bar"
msgstr "Vrstica stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: mainworkspace.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar shows messages and progress information. Most notably is the "
"currently selected schedule shown at the right of the status bar. Note that "
"most of the views in the <emphasis>Views</emphasis> category display "
"information depending on the selected schedule, so if the project is not "
"scheduled (<emphasis>Not Scheduled</emphasis>), most views will be empty."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica stanja prikazuje sporočila in informacije o napredku. Predvsem je "
"trenutno izbrani časovni plan prikazan na desni strani vrstice stanja. "
"Upoštevajte, da večina pogledov v kategoriji <emphasis>Pogledi</emphasis> "
"prikazuje informacije glede na izbrani plan, tako da če projekt ni načrtovan "
"(<emphasis>Ni razporejen</emphasis>), bo večina pogledov praznih."
